Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.93,0:00:11.16,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,最初的风啊  传递我的讯息
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.56,0:00:20.45,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,总是对你深信不疑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.71,0:00:29.77,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,那时站在梦里的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.39,0:00:37.62,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,环顾景色却有点望而却步
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.18,0:00:45.93,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,但我已决定头也不回的往前走
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.09,0:00:54.12,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,你是否也在仰望天空看那七色的彩虹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.68,0:01:02.57,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,最初的风啊  传递我的讯息
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.06,0:01:11.19,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,守护着那朝着梦想前进的背影
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.74,0:01:19.74,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,飞扬的风啊     追随着阳光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.24,0:01:29.81,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,挥着自由的翅膀勇敢地飞向天空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.51,0:23:36.50,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,总是很自由的你 现在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.82,0:23:43.18,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,在雨中追逐着怎样的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.64,0:23:48.46,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪里与孤独作斗争
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.78,0:23:54.28,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,强忍着眼泪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.90,0:24:05.89,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人也不要紧 你和我一样
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.62,0:24:17.43,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然净是绕远路 为什么喜欢这条路
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.10,0:24:23.73,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,感到幸福 高兴的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.17,0:24:29.26,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,因为想起你的事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.98,0:24:35.39,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,色彩鲜艳的季节一定能
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.53,0:24:42.18,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,传送这份思念
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.24,0:01:35.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,府库
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.64,0:01:40.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是坐落于彩云国皇宫一处颇为寂寞的房屋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.77,0:01:43.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和朝廷的政治没有什么联系
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.92,0:01:45.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个在积满灰尘的书籍中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.78,0:01:47.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只需要一味地管理
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.67,0:01:50.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,且不为人知的官职
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.99,0:01:53.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.70,0:01:56.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔  秀丽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.55,0:01:57.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起喝茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.95,0:01:59.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这位是蓝楸瑛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.42,0:02:01.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您认识的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.91,0:02:03.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…那当然
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.01,0:02:05.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎您 皇上…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.29,0:02:06.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,楸瑛大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.28,0:02:12.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邵可大人  您好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.06,0:02:14.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那  来一起喝茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.95,0:02:16.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝楸瑛大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.75,0:02:18.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.36,0:02:21.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先把手头的工作收拾一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.61,0:02:27.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二集 井底之蛙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.04,0:02:29.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  静兰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.49,0:02:32.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝将军？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.07,0:02:34.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请过来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.37,0:02:40.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这位是？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.85,0:02:42.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这位是李绛攸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.48,0:02:44.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在吏部工作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.41,0:02:46.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的老朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.21,0:02:47.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁是你的老朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.55,0:02:49.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和你的孽缘  我受够了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.86,0:02:51.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那位吏部侍郎吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.04,0:02:54.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,16岁就高中状元
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.52,0:02:56.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史上最年轻的吏部的侍郎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.92,0:02:59.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是绛攸 是名人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.99,0:03:03.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是上午不是吏部公务的时间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.30,0:03:05.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么就到府库这里来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.66,0:03:10.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来这里就是我们公务
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.44,0:03:11.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和你的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.64,0:03:13.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.27,0:03:15.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.31,0:03:18.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们和你一样都是侍奉皇上的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.22,0:03:22.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这个工作闲得发慌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.34,0:03:26.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是秀丽娘娘的佣人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.40,0:03:27.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.89,0:03:29.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,清闲的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.59,0:03:34.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就过来瞧瞧你家小姐的本事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.47,0:03:37.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请喝茶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.86,0:03:42.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好喝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.56,0:03:44.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事实上该是这个味道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.99,0:03:49.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一直都喝这么苦的『父亲茶』吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.11,0:03:51.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,『父亲茶』？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.29,0:03:55.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是父亲泡的苦的要死的茶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.15,0:03:59.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢邵可大人泡的『父亲茶』
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.37,0:04:01.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是善良的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.67,0:04:04.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,经常来府库的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.99,0:04:05.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.25,0:04:07.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为部下？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.78,0:04:13.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…你是红妃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.93,0:04:15.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 你知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.67,0:04:16.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.40,0:04:18.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天去后宫从珠翠这里听说的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.09,0:04:20.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.12,0:04:22.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去后宫有什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.01,0:04:26.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.57,0:04:28.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说有皇上的召见？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.90,0:04:29.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.34,0:04:31.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.67,0:04:33.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你们久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.93,0:04:36.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  邵可大人请喝茶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.24,0:04:41.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秀丽是红家的小姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.07,0:04:44.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么这么擅长做点心呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.05,0:04:46.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且这双…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.69,0:04:50.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这双手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.29,0:04:53.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都皲裂了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.20,0:04:55.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不像大小姐的手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.89,0:04:57.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使这样 自从进了皇宫以后
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.65,0:04:59.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经漂亮很多了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.87,0:05:01.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们家很穷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.12,0:05:05.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天都不得不工作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.61,0:05:08.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我的手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.96,0:05:12.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全不像别的小姐那样是又白又光滑的手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.92,0:05:16.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我觉得这也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.81,0:05:18.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲大人 静兰和我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.10,0:05:21.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了三人一起生活
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.25,0:05:22.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样很好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.14,0:05:24.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,静兰？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.27,0:05:26.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该在哪儿见过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.12,0:05:29.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被分配在皇上随从的左羽林军
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.16,0:05:32.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,零零碎碎地掉了好多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.71,0:05:34.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像个孩子一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.38,0:05:35.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经十九岁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.94,0:05:36.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是小孩了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.90,0:05:38.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.34,0:05:40.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和皇上一样的年纪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.91,0:05:41.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.91,0:05:46.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  你吃了几个了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.52,0:05:47.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概五 六个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.61,0:05:50.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃得太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.09,0:05:52.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打包给你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.63,0:05:54.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等会儿再吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.95,0:05:58.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秀丽真像个啰嗦的母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.21,0:06:01.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.17,0:06:03.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.50,0:06:07.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样也不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.87,0:06:18.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.96,0:06:27.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然 喜欢男人的传言是真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.39,0:06:28.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.89,0:06:30.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在这里做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.67,0:06:31.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.76,0:06:33.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是静兰啊 吓了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.23,0:06:38.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对皇上不去小姐的寝宫感到不满意？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.32,0:06:39.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说蠢话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.97,0:06:41.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.39,0:06:42.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.37,0:06:47.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人实际上是很寂寞的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.01,0:06:49.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这么觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.43,0:06:54.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次遇见那个人问他名字的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.65,0:06:56.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道他回答什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.79,0:06:58.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说是叫『蓝楸瑛』
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.41,0:06:59.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.91,0:07:03.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在皇宫也不穿官服 穿着便服能在皇宫晃荡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.12,0:07:06.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真奇怪这样的人怎么会是皇上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.68,0:07:09.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐  这些书是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.26,0:07:11.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 这些？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.11,0:07:13.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是想用来学习的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.18,0:07:17.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是作为皇上的教育指导者才进皇宫的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.83,0:07:19.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要有适当的准备
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.71,0:07:23.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原本以为是个不像样的昏庸皇上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.75,0:07:26.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和他说话后却又完全不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.19,0:07:27.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常的孩子气
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.81,0:07:30.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不发脾气也不傲慢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.56,0:07:31.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.10,0:07:33.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还好好地听我说话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.87,0:07:35.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能听别人讲话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.53,0:07:37.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得是能用言语沟通的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.00,0:07:39.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想像中的那么差
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.26,0:07:41.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.26,0:07:44.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定他能成为一个好皇上呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.89,0:07:45.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.85,0:07:47.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.88,0:07:49.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以不能不学习
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.57,0:07:57.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霄太师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.41,0:07:59.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.32,0:08:00.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是秀丽娘娘
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.06,0:08:03.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有件事情想拜托太师
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.46,0:08:04.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.54,0:08:06.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想读书
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.70,0:08:09.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但如果只是自己一个人读的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.24,0:08:11.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能否帮我介绍个老师呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.27,0:08:14.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔 明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.59,0:08:15.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包在我身上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.32,0:08:22.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先从朝廷构造的基础开始
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.33,0:08:26.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秀丽娘娘是霄太师请到皇宫的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.37,0:08:27.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.53,0:08:30.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,某些程度的知识看来是必须掌握的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.24,0:08:33.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么能说一说四省六部吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.93,0:08:34.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四省是指
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.74,0:08:38.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尚书省 门下省 中书省  仙洞省
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.72,0:08:40.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.24,0:08:42.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尚书省下面的六部
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.44,0:08:46.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包括吏部 户部 礼部 兵部 刑部 工部
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.15,0:08:48.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解的很详细呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.82,0:08:51.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我非常想参加国试
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.24,0:08:53.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直跟着父亲学习
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.08,0:08:56.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是因为女子不能成为官员
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.97,0:08:58.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便把梦想寄托在小孩子身上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.98,0:09:00.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在私塾里当老师
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.41,0:09:03.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经学过了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.71,0:09:04.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.73,0:09:05.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话现在开始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.17,0:09:08.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要学的东西就没什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.48,0:09:11.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 那倒不是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.75,0:09:16.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学问不是永无止境的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.13,0:09:23.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说来  蓝将军
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.08,0:09:25.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为武官的你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.81,0:09:27.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.43,0:09:29.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊..那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.91,0:09:31.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.09,0:09:35.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绛攸大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.60,0:09:37.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又迷路了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.58,0:09:41.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我正想代替你来执教呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.84,0:09:42.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.12,0:09:45.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他某些方面可以说是天才啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.24,0:09:49.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走路三十分钟就会迷路的大路痴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.46,0:09:51.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路痴？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.98,0:09:54.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喋喋不休的你烦死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.98,0:09:57.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的学生已经在等你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.47,0:09:59.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.85,0:10:05.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了这个国家而想读书才是正道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.73,0:10:07.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与此相比 那个昏君…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.44,0:10:09.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昏君？！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.29,0:10:12.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个皇宫虽说很大但也很小
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.02,0:10:14.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小怎么还迷路了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.92,0:10:15.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.99,0:10:19.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说的是那个昏君还什么都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.53,0:10:23.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连女子都为了国家而这么勤奋好学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.65,0:10:25.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昏君是绝对不会理朝的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.60,0:10:27.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别那么气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.20,0:10:28.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.92,0:10:29.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.91,0:10:31.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个昏君…呃不是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.04,0:10:35.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皇上的话 是不是没有出过皇宫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.90,0:10:37.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不太清楚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.03,0:10:38.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕是的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.57,0:10:40.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有美女陪伴着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.58,0:10:43.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会好好地在路上表现吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.51,0:10:45.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次就一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.55,0:10:47.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.13,0:10:49.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,井底之蛙怎知大海
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.44,0:10:51.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,见过世面后
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.16,0:10:53.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论是怎样的昏君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.45,0:10:55.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许会变得有点想执政吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.11,0:11:04.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秀丽的家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.25,0:11:05.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离这儿很近吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.39,0:11:06.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.20,0:11:11.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇  真是相当热闹的地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.62,0:11:13.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里有很多店哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.01,0:11:15.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,料理自不用说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.41,0:11:16.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古董啊  饰品啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.03,0:11:19.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衣服 书籍什么都有的卖
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.44,0:11:24.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔  请买两个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.28,0:11:26.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.23,0:11:29.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也要吃吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.14,0:11:36.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 很好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.26,0:11:38.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.52,0:11:41.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次一边走一边吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.53,0:11:44.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.75,0:11:49.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.42,0:11:52.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秀丽老师！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.43,0:11:54.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柳晋！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.19,0:11:57.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近去哪里了啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.56,0:11:59.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…有点事…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.99,0:12:00.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秀丽老师！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.17,0:12:02.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,静兰呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.06,0:12:04.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个花哨的哥哥是谁啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.08,0:12:08.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下完了 的确是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.91,0:12:12.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花哨那是…不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.79,0:12:18.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是静兰也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.33,0:12:20.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起来玩神社祭典游戏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.83,0:12:21.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玩吧玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.40,0:12:25.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秀丽老师！！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.24,0:12:29.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琴恋不好了！！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.23,0:12:39.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么劣质的梳子竟然那么贵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.10,0:12:40.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.25,0:12:41.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.33,0:12:44.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是黄杨木做的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.86,0:12:46.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个价钱已经便宜了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.63,0:12:49.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用嘴说的话随便你怎么吹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.76,0:12:52.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是　用嘴说的话随便你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.47,0:12:53.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.67,0:12:57.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道这个做工的精制
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.19,0:12:59.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还真是没有眼光啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.41,0:13:00.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.84,0:13:02.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你再纠缠下去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.34,0:13:04.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都会认为你耍无赖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.13,0:13:06.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样也不要紧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.42,0:13:10.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是呀　怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.56,0:13:14.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秀丽老师　谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.76,0:13:16.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么一点小事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.58,0:13:18.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起这个　你母亲怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.68,0:13:20.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.68,0:13:22.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她从早上起因为感冒一直睡着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.17,0:13:25.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你在看店啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.73,0:13:27.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.70,0:13:28.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有个好想法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.08,0:13:35.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  秀丽老师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.71,0:13:37.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,店就交给我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.50,0:13:39.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好好地照顾你母亲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.34,0:13:40.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.64,0:13:44.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好　要赚好多钱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.17,0:13:47.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.48,0:13:49.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要发簪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.17,0:13:53.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂　你也来喊几声
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.29,0:13:53.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.89,0:13:55.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是　我也要喊吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.72,0:13:59.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊　除了你还有谁啊　快
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.23,0:14:01.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.09,0:14:02.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,声音再大一点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.52,0:14:03.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.91,0:14:06.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀　真是个好男人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.23,0:14:08.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.60,0:14:10.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您看这个发簪怎么样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.22,0:14:14.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊　真的很不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.87,0:14:16.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给您特别优惠哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.45,0:14:19.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不试试看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.62,0:14:21.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来　帮她插到头发上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.25,0:14:26.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.42,0:14:27.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.31,0:14:30.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很适合您哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.12,0:14:32.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很适合您
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.06,0:14:34.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.08,0:14:35.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.09,0:14:40.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就买一个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.99,0:14:42.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.58,0:14:49.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能让那么好的男人亲手为我戴发簪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.74,0:14:51.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.50,0:14:52.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也替我选一个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.13,0:14:55.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家不要挤
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.32,0:14:56.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按顺序来 按顺序来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.64,0:15:01.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国王竟然在卖东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.59,0:15:04.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是假冒我的名字而受到的惩罚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.70,0:15:06.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶　那个是　静兰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.26,0:15:08.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是护卫官
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.95,0:15:11.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不近不远在暗中保护着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.38,0:15:16.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真期待直接参见主上的时刻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.62,0:15:20.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时候要好好地解恨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.48,0:15:23.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赚得可真不少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.55,0:15:27.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样琴恋母亲的药费也解决了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.96,0:15:30.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,累了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.90,0:15:32.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没　怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.92,0:15:33.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觉得很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.63,0:15:35.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.25,0:15:38.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能够帮助别人是很棒的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.98,0:15:43.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能够帮助别人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.81,0:15:46.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里就是我家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.37,0:15:55.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是很贫穷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.65,0:15:57.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊　真没有礼貌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.54,0:15:58.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.41,0:16:02.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了　反正也是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.52,0:16:09.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秀丽是孩子们的老师啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.95,0:16:10.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.32,0:16:12.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.01,0:16:14.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且也很会做生意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.35,0:16:20.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个是樱花吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.24,0:16:21.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯　是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.94,0:16:25.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我家的樱花已经不开花了　从八年前起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.41,0:16:28.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八年前？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.80,0:16:30.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八年前王位纷争的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.19,0:16:32.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国王驾崩后
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.00,0:16:35.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朝廷纷争不断　国事衰弱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.49,0:16:38.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住在城邑的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.00,0:16:40.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也同样过得很悲惨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.35,0:16:45.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很多贵族都紧闭大门
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.94,0:16:48.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,门口躺倒着很多饿死的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.31,0:16:50.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲和静兰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.83,0:16:53.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了镇上的人能生活下去尽量接济他们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.30,0:16:57.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我们也没有帮到什么忙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.73,0:17:01.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概最起作用的　是我们家院子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.51,0:17:03.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有很多结果的果树
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.55,0:17:05.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,池塘也很大
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.06,0:17:09.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以把果实和鱼分给镇上的居民
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.79,0:17:12.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此现在池塘里一条鱼也没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.56,0:17:14.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果子也是很久以前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.92,0:17:17.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为连花也不开了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.50,0:17:19.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部都吃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.66,0:17:24.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很多人就在我眼前死去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.98,0:17:27.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小秀丽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.46,0:17:30.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了这个孩子能拉一曲二胡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.13,0:17:33.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他好好安息
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.74,0:17:34.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日复一日
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.29,0:17:37.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不停地拉着二胡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.43,0:17:40.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直就像是为了死亡而活着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.95,0:17:46.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们究竟为什么要忍受这样的回忆而活着？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.10,0:17:50.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲和静兰也日益消瘦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.59,0:17:53.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我当时很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.01,0:17:56.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两个人都死了只留下我一人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.20,0:17:57.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每晚都做着这个梦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.51,0:18:01.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是恐怖的日子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.07,0:18:03.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秀丽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.64,0:18:07.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我进了王宫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.37,0:18:09.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经厌烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.32,0:18:12.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都做不了 面对着自己的无力而叹息的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.74,0:18:13.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.46,0:18:15.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次如果是我能够做到的事的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.74,0:18:17.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要做
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.53,0:18:21.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己的愿望什么的没有什么了不起的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.97,0:18:25.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不想说"请让国家的每个人都过上幸福的生活"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.78,0:18:27.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任何傻话都不想说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.89,0:18:32.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸福和不幸都是各人自身的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.58,0:18:36.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以王不必担负那样的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.40,0:18:39.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人的人生是他自己的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.65,0:18:43.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须自己去选择道路活着走下去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.10,0:18:45.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己…选择
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.58,0:18:50.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的选择　难以做出的时候也是有的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.33,0:18:53.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是天灾的话只有放弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.92,0:18:55.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是是人灾的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.32,0:18:56.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就应该可以用人的力量去防止
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.61,0:18:59.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以　去了王宫？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.83,0:19:00.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.00,0:19:04.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用人的力量能够办到的事有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.78,0:19:09.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但平民的话即使很努力也有很多事办不到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.46,0:19:11.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个就是国王的工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.08,0:19:14.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,王如果也逃避了那要由谁来做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.25,0:19:20.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不知道他为什么不理朝政
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.04,0:19:23.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但既然我已经跟随了王就没有办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.74,0:19:25.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要让他努力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.95,0:19:29.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相对的　我也要努力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.00,0:19:30.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.31,0:19:32.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为最小的皇子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.61,0:19:35.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果说没有学过怎么治理国家的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.29,0:19:36.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就和他一起学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.21,0:19:39.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不安的时候我在身边
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.10,0:19:41.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想发牢骚的话 无论多少我都会听
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.63,0:19:43.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想哭的时候哭就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.34,0:19:47.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是大臣　不用在我面前装样子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.60,0:19:49.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是为了生孩子来的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.47,0:19:52.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不只是为了让你一个人做好而来的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.23,0:19:55.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是来支持你的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.46,0:19:56.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在你的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.59,0:19:58.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮助你成为一个真正的王
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.39,0:20:04.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果遇到王的话我想像这样说的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.18,0:20:06.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是根本见不到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.12,0:20:08.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和王认识的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.67,0:20:11.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能帮我转达刚刚的话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.80,0:20:12.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.86,0:20:14.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果想做的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.51,0:20:18.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉他我明天下午在府库等他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.82,0:20:23.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.83,0:20:25.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定转告他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.01,0:20:33.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茶凉了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.66,0:20:34.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再去沏茶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.02,0:20:44.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.93,0:20:50.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,静兰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.99,0:20:58.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好好努力了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.68,0:21:00.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些日子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.16,0:21:03.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八年前的事只是回想起来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.61,0:21:05.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也很伤心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.06,0:21:14.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.15,0:21:16.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经不要紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.12,0:21:20.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主上明天一定会驾临府库的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.84,0:21:37.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朕就是紫刘辉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.68,0:21:40.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和朕很熟的男子给我传话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.51,0:21:46.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那　回答呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.00,0:21:49.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起从政吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.31,0:21:52.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.07,0:22:04.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问你一个问题可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.10,0:22:05.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.98,0:22:10.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相较女人你更喜欢男人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.97,0:22:11.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.62,0:22:13.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.10,0:22:18.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧　太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.72,0:22:21.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个　虽然有继承人的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.38,0:22:23.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但好好想想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.87,0:22:26.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我们先来学习政事的基础吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.23,0:22:33.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就介绍老师了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.84,0:22:36.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于见到您了  我感到很荣幸　主上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.09,0:22:39.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是李绛攸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.47,0:22:42.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要努力啊  主上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.83,0:22:44.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝楸瑛你怎么在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.00,0:22:48.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的职责本来就是王的护卫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.33,0:22:52.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且　听说最近在府库有人冒充我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.63,0:22:54.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以来看下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.87,0:22:58.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从现在起  我会尽我所能地来指导您
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.22,0:23:00.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您可要有觉悟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.29,0:23:02.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那就拜托你了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.62,0:23:05.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主上终于开始从政了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.21,0:23:11.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来让秀丽小姐入宫真是做对了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.28,0:23:14.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊　对于你来说算是出了个好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.82,0:23:17.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对你来说这话是多余的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.34,0:23:17.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来就要看
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.27,0:23:23.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主上是不是给李绛攸蓝楸瑛机会了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.03,0:24:56.03,CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,500)}真人不露相
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.56,0:24:49.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刘辉去做的话就能做好的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.13,0:24:50.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点对他改观了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.44,0:24:53.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要得意哦 还没有完全做好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.15,0:24:54.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是怎么到我的睡房来了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.13,0:24:57.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明叫你不要得意忘形的
